metadata.name: Million Cutz #1
metadata.description: Millioncutz is a collection of 3,333 scratch music NFTs minted on the Ethereum blockchain and created by the youngest ever world DMC DJ champion,DJ RENA. Each NFT is created by generativizing DJ REAN's scratched stem data with a special audio engine and combined with a QR code for the original piece. However, Millioncutz is not just a music NFT for scratch enthusiasts; Millioncutz is the key to musical creativity and a web3 social experience for its holders.
